Now, this is Leicester Dolokhune, 3rd in 60. We have a dollenging of the Skiall, or it's a few hundredus to Skiall. And I'm one, Muncher in Rahn. And there, von Lear, Tales of the Seal People, with the Donogogogicilliam. And it's it's a the other Nus MacNeil and there are a cupid as Rupertchunach on an Erielle. Hewere a skil on a Gaelic for a henever. The club on a bala-beak to the Gaelthach. He clach-oog of the club on a comag crea to the Gailtach Thee Chalk Uigh Ongsuch on the CUMIG CUMIG CRIE in the Fakhlain Scrifee to Malcolm and Mary Gou Callum and Mary was the script of Anne Berla I'm I'd I'd Dahlavhe I'm Acklevin'a in Gronikive, he car annosach. O'hyunate, there's chowluch of furich, Tewa'vachlattie, faxed at allah, and reichroch, and e'iske, a ch'is'lonia-ach, carich. She callum a ver a vire, M'er A' name, and she Mary, the very few. It's the first of one, and she's a few hours gumma, and she clown Iarski, a vuntah. It's got to my father. Hanick jirich in route itter. Hane itchirch on route itter. Fegmari, a taring, a callum, on the colus arctic cussia, in the chush-yesh. It was, in Leigh, Moore. Mokreach, a callum, chanagy, ha coles greti, on the orstack-vour-achard. Channier lessach it, chanag the brahad, soan this a ruckugugue me. Now, there is Callum four way to the o'eran a hickick to Mare a hickickickil Ere A chalim, chaned mary as, as scourou chanagm, Mary, as a scourou, chanathe, gus the bough hathen not ron, and chanagalim to bega in the tachrachan. Then the tachan soas a clon soas, and gacket the school at o'us kheath-ge Cahlem a chutuch-ahed with the nigher, Raincheekhah with the Neher, ryanethehaheufth in the line vohrae. Fisgara was this, to a omichieuah, ack on the nether, Eirich, Sturm, Gung Rowe Hounda at the Bata and it imberug in the Junae but chawet imurag in the Chira, but charoot loa, Gle-or, chahe'en-saic a churn, Bunas-Kyum. It's aher chalim, ma'u'er in love, and it was phoiseechalmhean, fire-chumish, as nabatard. "'Cach verka heine, Efe, Snav Guthier. Getta, the Rannica in Clotoch, charro Skial, to the vach. Chahegachie, Rue Aven and the Nien Gaiunzi, Tullichter a heart Beal. Katt's Ferem, hootarded. Not, he'll a call-der-o'rt. Then it's the one, that one, callum, callum, it's a good, in de law, in de law, and you'lla in one you there, or co-yueo on the chute. But, you'd d'allorak at Datt. In J. Gron, Shachanan, you Marii, he'd do you dune, he's the big, chary, Cautium. He'd ganyal, and cusach on the Trey, a-o-o-o-o--mach-mach-gum- I mean the Charii Cuthum. He'd genie a cussock on the Tray, a coitamac, Goumoud. It's a Cria, Bristia. Lurok Ihaar in Chaheck to the Chathach. It was a hast slain. He'llian, Duneascah, but there's very a very much be a man o'numulad. He'd rio giri but there were Mare, Voch, bough, bough, on the mullet. Charrhoe I gire to bring to the dunya. Lah of this a time, there is a good one, and I'll give my one in the Alighihtier.
